  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Assistance for Displaced and Returnee Afghan Migrants, and Humanitarian Data Collection</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IOM project has three key elements: strengthening of water, sanitation and hygiene support with a focus on women and girls, across four priority provinces; provision of humanitarian assistance in and around border crossing points with Iran and Pakistan for 3,000 returnees and vulnerable Afghans displaced around the border crossing-points who are in need of immediate assistance; and implementation of Displacement Tracking in Afghanistan to inform programming for IOM and across the humanitarian system in Afghanistan.</narrative>
  </description>
